<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Reçu de Paiement - Airmess</title>
    <style>
        @page {
            margin: 10mm;
        }
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.3;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .receipt-container {
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .receipt-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #f8f9fa);
        }
        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .receipt-title {
            text-align: right;
        }
        .receipt-title h2 {
            color: #4158D0;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .receipt-title p {
            color: #777;
            margin: 3px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .receipt-body {
            padding: 15px 20px;
        }
        .reference-number {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #EDF2FF;
            border: 1px dashed #4158D0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4158D0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .details-grid {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .details-section {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        .details-section h3 {
            color: #4158D0;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .details-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .details-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
        }
        .reservation-details {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .reservation-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #e0e0e0;
        }
        .reservation-table th {
            background-color: #4158D0;
            color: white;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 8px 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .reservation-table td {
            padding: 8px 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .reservation-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .total-section {
            background-color: #EDF2FF;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .total-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .total-amount {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #4158D0;
        }
        .receipt-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .receipt-footer p {
            margin: 3px 0;
        }
        .watermark {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-45deg);
            font-size: 80px;
            color: rgba(65, 88, 208, 0.05);
            z-index: 0;
            white-space: nowrap;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .small-text {
            font-size: 11px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="receipt-container">
        <div class="receipt-header">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <svg width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 800 800" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <defs>
                        <linearGradient id="logoBg" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#e9f0f4" />
                            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#f4e4e0" />
                        </linearGradient>
                        <linearGradient id="logoA" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#5b8cca" />
                            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#4a5ebb" />
                        </linearGradient>
                        <linearGradient id="logoOrange" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
                            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f7941d" />
                            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#ffb366" />
                        </linearGradient>
                        <linearGradient id="logoPlane" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#6dbdf6" />
                            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#a6daf2" />
                        </linearGradient>
                    </defs>
                    
                    <!-- Background Circle -->
                    <circle cx="400" cy="400" r="400" fill="url(#logoBg)" />
                    
                    <!-- Letter A -->
                    <path d="M300,200 L400,500 L500,200 L600,500 L700,500 L550,100 L450,100 L300,500 L200,500 L300,200" fill="url(#logoA)" />
                    
                    <!-- Swirl -->
                    <path d="M150,350 Q250,200 400,300 Q550,400 650,250" stroke="url(#logoOrange)" stroke-width="40" fill="none" />
                    
                    <!-- Plane -->
                    <path d="M650,250 L700,200 L650,150 L600,250 L650,250 Z" fill="url(#logoPlane)" />
                    <path d="M620,220 L650,180 L600,200 L620,220 Z" fill="white" opacity="0.6" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="receipt-title">
                <h2>REÇU DE PAIEMENT</h2>
                <p>Date d'émission : {{ date|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="receipt-body">
            <div class="reference-number">
                Référence : RC-{{ reservation.idR }}-{{ date|date('Ymd') }}
            </div>
            
            <div class="details-grid">
                <div class="details-section">
                    <h3>INFORMATIONS CLIENT</h3>
                    <div class="details-row">
                        <span class="details-label">Nom :</span>
                        <span>{{ reservation.user.name }} {{ reservation.user.prenom }}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="details-row">
                        <span class="details-label">Email :</span>
                        <span class="small-text">{{ reservation.user.email }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="details-section">
                    <h3>INFORMATIONS DE PAIEMENT</h3>
                    <div class="details-row">
                        <span class="details-label">Date de transaction :</span>
                        <span>{{ reservation.dateRes|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="details-row">
                        <span class="details-label">Méthode :</span>
                        <span>Carte bancaire</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="details-row">
                        <span class="details-label">Statut :</span>
                        <span style="color: #2dce89; font-weight: bold;">PAYÉ</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="reservation-details">
                <table class="reservation-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th width="60%">Description</th>
                            <th>Période</th>
                            <th>Montant</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                {{ reservation.offre.description }}<br>
                                <small style="color: #777;">{{ reservation.offre.place }}</small>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                {% if reservation.offre.startDate %}
                                    {{ reservation.offre.startDate|date('d/m/Y') }}
                                    {% if reservation.offre.endDate %}
                                        <br>au {{ reservation.offre.endDate|date('d/m/Y') }}
                                    {% endif %}
                                {% else %}
                                    N/A
                                {% endif %}
                            </td>
                            <td>{{ reservation.offre.priceAfter }} €</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            
            <div class="total-section">
                <span class="total-label">TOTAL PAYÉ</span>
                <span class="total-amount">{{ reservation.offre.priceAfter }} €</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="receipt-footer">
            <p>Ce reçu est généré automatiquement et constitue une preuve de paiement.</p>
            <p>&copy; {{ date|date('Y') }} Airmess. Tous droits réservés. Pour toute assistance: support@airmess.com</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="watermark">PAYÉ</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 